{"about_the_game":"Monsters \u2018til Midnight is an arcade-inspired steampunk survival game all about powering up!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Weapons and Abilities</h2><br>From weaponized cucumber sandwiches to explosive crumpets, wield a diverse arsenal of both automatic, and manually aimed weaponry. Augment them with various powers and special abilities to make each run feel unique and challenging.<br><br>Aquire gold to purchase permanent upgrades that will further boost your destructive power.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/catterick_forest.gif?t=1698878918\" /><br><br>Work towards unlocking new playable characters, new zones, and devastating secret weapons each time you play.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/mtm_character_lineup_with_bars.png?t=1698878918\" /><br><br>Discover, equip, and trigger potent active abilities. Whether it\u2019s the defensive dodge roll, or devastating chimney brush attack, there\u2019s something for every playstyle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Local Co-op</h2><br>Join forces with a friend and play locally in 2 player co-op!* XP is shared between both players, so power up and fight the hordes of darkness together. If overwhelmed, spend a level upgrade to revive your teammate. <br><br>*<i>A controller is required for local multiplayer.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/MtM_coop_intercut.gif?t=1698878918\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defeat Time Itself</h2><br>Survive the ceaseless enemy onslaught until midnight, and face the deathly chimes of the death clocks! Can you defeat time itself?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/MtM_midnight_deathclocks.gif?t=1698878918\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"